description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 2 of 4 of the Live April match-up between The Ninjas and The Goddesses.
Vendetta is unstoppable, she is a terminator on a mission and that mission is to destroy Isis Love. Vendetta totally dominated Isis during their one-on-ones. She fingers Isis at will, and makes her moan on the mat. The Goddesses were over matched and defeated by a margin unheard of in Tag Team Wrestling. The Ninjas came to kick ass and they did! Tara Lynn Foxx performed splendidly and The Ninjas are undefeated in Tag Team action.
title: ROUND THREE
